text: Tuimalealiifano Va'aleto'a Eti Sualauvi II (born 29 April 1947) is a Samoan politician who is the current O le Ao o le Malo (head of state) of Samoa, in office since 2017. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:O le Ao o le Malo of Samoa
title: Tuimalealiʻifano Vaʻaletoʻa Sualauvi II
